    "title": "京东规则动态一览（2025年5月19日-2025年5月23日）",
    "followRuleId": "1241950714268356608",
    "content": "<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则公示】</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1236875511880355840&amp;btype=14\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年京东开放平台618</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">活动总则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">①调整预热期和开门红活动节奏：<span style=\"color: black;\">预热期-2025年5月28日00:00:00-2025年5月30日19:59:59；开门红-2025年5月30日20:00:00-2025年6月3日23:59:59；②增加跨店满减、官方立减、送礼专享折扣活动玩法。</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1236874775238938624&amp;btype=14\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年京东开放平台618</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">大促主题活动招商规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">调整活动节奏：预热时间-2025年5月28日00:00:00-2025年5月30日19:59:59；活动时间-2025年5月30日20:00:00-2025年6月20日23:59:59；打标时间-2025年5月28日00:00:00-2025年6月20日23:59:59。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1243119871856873472&amp;btype=14\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年京东开放平台618</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">大促跨店满减活动规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">本次京东618主推每满200元减30元的跨店满减力度，促销生效期间，商家的同一款商品可全程参与，重点鼓励全品类商家参与，并着重鼓励商家以全店商品形式报名。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1243142926234685440&amp;btype=14\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年京东开放平台618</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">大促官方立减活动规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">官方立减是一种按类目设置折扣百分比的单品维度促销玩法，本次京东618分为5%、10%、15%三档的优惠力度。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1243118503901401088&amp;btype=14\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年京东开放平台618</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">大促送礼专享折扣活动规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">本次京东618主推送礼专享折扣85折促销，促销生效期间，商家的同一款商品可全程参与，积极参与送礼专享折扣活动可更高效促进礼赠类商品的销售增长。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;\">6</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: #333333;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1243146754606632960&amp;btype=14\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年京东开放平台超级补贴日活动总则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">年京东超级补贴日作为京东S级活动，活动时间：（1）预热时间：2025年5月28日00:00:00-2025年5月28日19:59:59；（2）活动时间：2025年5月28日20:00:00-2025年5月29日23:59:59。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">7</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1237975736313319424&amp;btype=14\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年京东开放平台心动购物季活动总则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">调整活动节奏：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">预热时间-2025年05月13日00:00:00-2025年05月13日19:59:59；活动时间-2025年05月13日20:00:00-2025年05月27日23:59:59。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">8</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【修订】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1237969251839643648&amp;btype=14\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《2025</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">年京东开放平台心动购物季主题活动招商规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-weight: normal;\">调整活动节奏：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">预热时间-2025年05月13日00:00:00-2025年05月13日19:59:59；活动时间-2025年05月13日20:00:00-2025年05月27日23:59:59。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">9</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1242657825470156800&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台安心品质文胸商品认证标准》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">明确文胸类商品品质推优标准，包括材质、功能、性能分级等要求。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">10</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1242681751785050112&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台安心品质睡衣商品认证标准》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">明确睡衣类商品品质推优标准，包括材质、功能、性能分级等要求。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">11</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1241630992670789632\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台隐私发货规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">指定类目的商家（健康类类目），应默认支持&ldquo;隐私发货&rdquo;，需按照相应服务规范为消费者提供隐私发货的服务保障。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">12</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1241947055799275520&amp;btype=6\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《拍拍二手店铺命名规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">明确拍拍二手不同类型店铺的名称要求。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">13</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/list.action?btype=6&amp;bid=1187220917353320448&amp;useId=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《拍拍二手商品质量检测定级标准》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">对手机、平板、手表等明确检测标准。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">14</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1241949170928062464&amp;btype=6\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《拍拍商品送检规范》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">明确送检商家、检测服务商收发规范，检测要求及检测流程。</span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">15</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">、【新增】</span><a style=\"color: blue; text-decoration: underline;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1241952883553996800&amp;btype=6\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台二手商品类目全托管服务规则》</span></a></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin-right: 0cm; margin-left: 0cm; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">明确二手类目商家参加全托管服务的规则，包括全托管服务内容，商家需满足的条件等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 24.0pt; line-height: 200%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">【规则生效】</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">1</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【修订】</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1239485407964565504\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台店铺综合体验分规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; background: white;\">五星店铺认证其他特殊要求</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">调整。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">2</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【新增】</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1239906324435832832\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《关于粽子商品价格及包装管理的公告》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">对单价超过500元的盒装粽子实行重点监管，商家应当确保销售单价超过500元单品/盒装粽子的价格合理性。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">3</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【修订】</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1238011423397908480&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台发货管理规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">调整关于商家发货时效的要求，修订后，若商家承诺的发货时效&le;2天（当日、24h、48h），则要求商家在消费者完成支付的2天内完成发货即可。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">关联规则：</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1239414283402612736&amp;btype=12\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台个人个体交易管理规则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">4</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【新增】</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1239487186232020992&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台发布违禁商品及信息管理规范-</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">刀枪实施细则》等实施细则</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">对违禁商品及信息管理规范增加实施细则，包括军警、野生动植物、未成年等。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">5</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">、【修订】</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1239751285499105280&amp;btype=1\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台商家套利细则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">核心内容：</span></strong><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">补充商家套利中的&ldquo;商家&rdquo;定义，包括商家加盟门店等关联机构。</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin: 0cm; line-height: 200%; background: white; font-size: 12pt; font-family: 宋体;\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black;\">关联规则：【修订】</span><span style=\"color: black;\"><a style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: blue;\" href=\"https://rule.jd.com/rule/ruleDetail.action?ruleId=1239751285499105280\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\">《京东开放平台商家违规管理总则》</span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"line-height: 200%; margin: 0cm; text-align: justify; font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 等线;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"floorcontent\" class=\"b-content\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: #000000; font-family: 'PingFang SC', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, 'Hiragino Sans GB', SimSun, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal; background-color: #ffffff;\" data-v-80c9ee8c=\"\">\n<div id=\"article-content\" class=\"editorContent\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" data-v-80c9ee8c=\"\"></div>\n</div>",
